column5: Ano pong work nyo? 31 na ko pero earning 32k lang. Bigla akong nagka anxiety. Dito ako sa Cebu kasi nagwo work. Ganyan na ba kalaki ang rates sa Manila? I am contmeplating din kasi na super underpaid na sguro ako at bumalik na ng Maynila. Thank you in advance.
HAHAHAHAHAHA pota this made my day.

I ma having anxiety after losing money in the stock market, frustrated sa job increase and caught in between resigning or waiting for another 3 years to get my retirement. (Our company requires 10years of service before getting the retirement fund)

I am a member of the Traders Lounge group sa FB and walang nagha-hype dun unlike any other groups I joined before. The advocacy of the admins and the founder is to teach totally for free. Walang paid mentorship, bash or hype. Di ako admin ng group, I just wanna attest na marami akong natutunan in less than a month in joining. I hope my fellow newbie can reach this, wag papaloko sa mga guru-guruan.

I suggest you try to learn first before jumping into investments. Read this to help yourself:

[https://gandakohpersonaltrading.home.blog/2020/01/19/only-average-down-on-stocks-with-good-fundamentals-is-an-ignorant-advice/](https://gandakohpersonaltrading.home.blog/2020/01/19/only-average-down-on-stocks-with-good-fundamentals-is-an-ignorant-advice/)
